comment: Added 'down-right-from-square', 'up-right-from-square', and 'file-arrow-curved-right' icons. Marked 'share-square' (use the 'up-right-from-square' icon instead) and 'file-export' (use the 'file-arrow-curved-right' icon instead) icons as deprecated. The deprecated icons will be removed in a future major release.
